lead_paragraph: China's Suning Commerce Group is leading a race to buy UK-based Stellar Group, one of the world's leading soccer agencies, a person with knowledge of the talks said, even as the retail giant is set to also invest in Italian club Inter Milan.

headline.print_headline: China's Suning Leads Race for Soccer 'Super Agent' Stellar-Source
